{"tid":140091,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［1Q] 超難 慎入 自問聰明先入","createTime":"2017-03-02T03:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T03:20:38.000Z","uid":23564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"037114217b29fb123ec4cc79f58b4ec1abf3fbc7","tid":140091,"uid":23564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"繼上次虎父無犬子後 小弟屙屎既時候又諗到條1Q考下全能既連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說慧珊 思達 明詩 就參選左腥港小姐 仲入去左總決賽<br />\n去到全場最期待既泳衣環節 評判們一睇就立即DQ左其中一個參選者 原因係佢竟然係一個人妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題就係 到底邊個比人DQ同點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上次就去到第三頁開估 今次睇下大家表現 太難會比提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f3e2d956e78964b5a37516b03829b5cf1dab54","tid":140091,"uid":284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"達明一派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e79dd908697eb5489a16d6f13956036799bbc39","tid":140091,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"思達 因為真係達哥去參選"},{"pid":"7f700d8023e27310f2bb861e45ac2d696181bc27","tid":140091,"uid":23564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>達明一派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n達明一派係咪姐係兩個都比人DQ?"},{"pid":"7d00fcf4b83dd009d84cdb4cb6c5e91cffb9cedb","tid":140091,"uid":23564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>思達 因為真係達哥去參選</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係達哥 只係一個好似達哥既人"},{"pid":"197555b1c1dfa18ff473951aea954a0d66843bfc","tid":1